Shader "==PGAME==/LobbyPlayer/m_lob_PlayerPBRHairColorFelt_lv3" {
Properties {

_BumpMapNr ("Normal Map(RGB)Matelness(A)", 2D) = "bump" { }
_BumpMapNr2 ("Normal Map(RGB)AO(A)", 2D) = "bump" { }

[Toggle] _Mask ("If Mask(打开遮罩)", Float) = 0
[Toggle] _Emissive ("If Emissive(打开自发光)", Float) = 0
[KeywordEnum(UV0, UV1)] _SLUV ("贴图采样UV选择", Float) = 0
[Header(Common)] _actorscale ("actor Scale(角色衰减缩放)", Float) = 1
[HideInInspector] _ActorScaleAttribute ("_ActorScaleAttribute", Float) = 1

_EmisssionScale ("EmisssionScale(自发光强度)", Range(0, 10)) = 0
_MainlightAttenuation ("MainlightAttenuation(主光源衰减)", Range(0.04, 32)) = 0.04
[KeywordEnum(X, Y, Z)] _AtVector ("AttenuationVector(衰减方向)", Float) = 0
[Header(HairHighlight)] _HairMap ("HairShape(R)Mask(G)", 2D) = "black" { }
_shapeST ("shapeST", Vector) = (1,1,0,0)
_SunShiftOffuse1 ("SunShiftOffuse1", Range(-1, 1)) = 0
_SunShiftOffuse2 ("SunShiftOffuse2", Range(-1, 1)) = 0

[HDR] _specularColor1 ("Specular1 Color", Color) = (0.2,0.2,0.2,1)
_glossiness_1X ("Specular1 X Axis", Range(0, 1)) = 0.1

_glossiness_2Y ("Specular2 Y Axis", Range(0, 1)) = 1
[Header(SH)] [KeywordEnum(Cla, Lerp)] _SHType ("SH Type(SH类型)", Float) = 1
_SHScale ("SHScale(SH强弱)", Range(0, 10)) = 1
[HDR] _SHTopColor ("SHTopColor(亮部颜色)", Color) = (2.5,2.5,2.5,1)
[HDR] _SHBotColor ("SHBotColor(暗部颜色)", Color) = (2.5,2.5,2.5,1)
[Header(OutLine)] [KeywordEnum(OFF, ON)] _VTEX ("是否使用贴图控制定点色", Float) = 0
[KeywordEnum(OFF, ON)] _VCOLOR2N ("是否使用顶点色勾边优化", Float) = 0
_OutlineMap ("OutlineMap(勾边贴图)", 2D) = "white" { }
_OutlineColor ("OutlineColor(勾边颜色)", Color) = (0.5,0.5,0.5,1)
_Offset ("Z Offset(深度偏移)", Float) = -5
_lightDir ("lightDirtion(勾边光源方向)", Vector) = (9.48,3.68,0,0)
[Header(MaskColor)] [HDR] _color1 ("_color1", Color) = (1,1,1,1)
[HDR] _color2 ("_color2", Color) = (1,1,1,1)
[HDR] _color3 ("_color3", Color) = (1,1,1,1)
[HDR] _color4 ("_color4", Color) = (1,1,1,1)
_metalv4 ("_metalv4", Vector) = (0,0,0,0)
_roughv4 ("_roughv4", Vector) = (1,1,1,1)
[KeywordEnum(OFF, Deffiuse, Normal, Metal, Roughness, AO, Emiss, SH)] _Debug ("textureDebug", Float) = 0
[HideInInspector] _Cull ("Vector1 ", Float) = 2

_ReceiveShadows ("Receive Shadows", Float) = 1

SubShader {

 Tags { "IGNOREPROJECTOR" = "true" "QUEUE" = "Geometry" "RenderPipeline" = "LightweightPipeline" "RenderType" = "Opaque" }

  ZTest Off
  ZWrite Off
  Cull Off
  GpuProgramID 54958
Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles3 " {
Keywords { "ENABLE_POST_TONE" "_ADDITIONAL_LIGHTS" "_ATVECTOR_Y" "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHADOWS_SOFT" "_SHTYPE_LERP" "_SLUV_UV1" }
"// hash: 8583d1688bf71290
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 300 es

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION

#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _HairMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD1.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat0.y);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShift;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _shapeST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FresnelColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _faceshadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _BumpMapNr2_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _colorSkin;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr2;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _HairMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec4 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
vec3 u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
vec2 u_xlat16;
mediump float u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
float u_xlat32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat48;
float u_xlat51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
mediump float u_xlat16_53;
mediump float u_xlat16_54;
mediump float u_xlat16_55;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _Mask * u_xlat16_1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_17<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_17<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat2.xy,u_xlat2.z);
    u_xlat2.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat3.xy,u_xlat3.z);
    u_xlat2.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat3.xy,u_xlat3.z);
    u_xlat2.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat3.xy,u_xlat3.z);
    u_xlat2.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_17 = dot(u_xlat2, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_33 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_33;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb0 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_17 = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_17;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_17) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD8.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_0.wwww + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_2 = -abs(u_xlat16_2) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2 = min(max(u_xlat16_2, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2 = clamp(u_xlat16_2, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + (-_colorSkin.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _colorSkin.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_2, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_53 = dot(u_xlat16_2, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_3.w + u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 + u_xlat16_2.w;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_2.w + (-u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_6.x + u_xlat16_52;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_52 = min(max(u_xlat16_52, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_52 = clamp(u_xlat16_52, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 2.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xzw) * vec3(u_xlat16_52) + u_xlat16_1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xw = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _shapeST.xy + _shapeST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xw).x;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_54 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_54 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_54);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_54) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_11.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_11.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_3.w + (-u_xlat16_53);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_54 + u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_54 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_53 = max(u_xlat16_53, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_53 = min(u_xlat16_53, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_53) * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat2.zw = vec2(u_xlat16_53) * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat2.xyyw * u_xlat2.xyxz;
    u_xlat16.xy = u_xlat2.zw * u_xlat2.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat48 / u_xlat10.y;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat48 / u_xlat16.y;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat51;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz / u_xlat8.zzz;
    u_xlat15.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BumpMapNr2_ST.xy + _BumpMapNr2_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = texture(_BumpMapNr2, u_xlat15.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * vec3(-1.0, -1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + (-u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_55 = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_55 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_55);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_55) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.z;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = max(u_xlat8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat16.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat32 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = max(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _HairMap_ST.xy + _HairMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xy).y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.x = log2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat0.x = exp2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot((-u_xlat13.xyz), u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * (-u_xlat16_5.xxx) + (-u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = abs(u_xlat16_7.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(u_xlat16_7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat16_53) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_23);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_0.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_23 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_52) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_53) + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_53 + 1.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat51 * u_xlat51;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat48) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_5.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_52 = min(max(u_xlat16_52, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_52 = clamp(u_xlat16_52, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_52 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * u_xlat16_5.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xzw + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_1.xzw + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw * vec3(u_xlat16_17);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_54) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

}
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "ENABLE_POST_TONE" "_ADDITIONAL_LIGHTS" "_ATVECTOR_Y" "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHADOWS_SOFT" "_SHTYPE_LERP" "_SLUV_UV1" }
"// hash: 8983ad6f9ee3afb1
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _MainlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump float _AddlightLerp;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD1.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat0.y);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat10_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _Mask * u_xlat16_1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_Cutoff);
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_17<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat2.z;
    u_xlat2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat3.z;
    u_xlat2.y = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat3.z;
    u_xlat2.z = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat3.z;
    u_xlat2.w = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = dot(u_xlat2, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_33 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb0 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_17 = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_17;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_17) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD8.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat10_0.wwww + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_2 = -abs(u_xlat16_2) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
    u_xlat16_2 = clamp(u_xlat16_2, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.yyy * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat10_3 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_3.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + (-_colorSkin.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _colorSkin.xyz;

    u_xlat16_53 = dot(u_xlat16_2, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat10_3.w + u_xlat16_53;

    u_xlat16_52 = clamp(u_xlat16_52, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 2.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xzw) * vec3(u_xlat16_52) + u_xlat16_1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xw = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _shapeST.xy + _shapeST.zw;
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xw).x;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat10_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat10_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_54 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_54 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_54);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_54) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_11.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_11.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat10_3.w + (-u_xlat16_53);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat10_0.y * u_xlat16_54 + u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat10_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_54 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_53 = max(u_xlat16_53, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_53 = min(u_xlat16_53, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_53) * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat2.zw = vec2(u_xlat16_53) * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat2.xyyw * u_xlat2.xyxz;
    u_xlat16.xy = u_xlat2.zw * u_xlat2.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat48 / u_xlat10.y;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat48 / u_xlat16.y;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat51;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz / u_xlat8.zzz;
    u_xlat15.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BumpMapNr2_ST.xy + _BumpMapNr2_ST.zw;
    u_xlat10_15.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMapNr2, u_xlat15.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat10_15.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * vec3(-1.0, -1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + (-u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_55 = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_55 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_55);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_55) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.z;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = max(u_xlat8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat16.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat32 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = max(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _HairMap_ST.xy + _HairMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xy).y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = log2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat0.x = exp2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + _ShadowOffset;
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot((-u_xlat13.xyz), u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * (-u_xlat16_5.xxx) + (-u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = abs(u_xlat16_7.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(u_xlat16_7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat16_53) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_0 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_23);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat10_0.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_23 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_52) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_53) + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_53 + 1.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat51 * u_xlat51;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;

    u_xlat16_21.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat48) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_5.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = clamp(u_xlat16_52, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_52 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * u_xlat16_5.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xzw + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_1.xzw + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw * vec3(u_xlat16_17);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_54) * u_xlat10_3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1Y;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _shapeST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _faceshadowScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _colorSkin;

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr2;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _HairMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec4 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
vec3 u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
vec2 u_xlat16;
mediump float u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
float u_xlat32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat48;
float u_xlat51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
mediump float u_xlat16_53;
mediump float u_xlat16_54;
mediump float u_xlat16_55;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _Mask * u_xlat16_1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_17<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_17<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat2.xy,u_xlat2.z);
    u_xlat2.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat3.xy,u_xlat3.z);
    u_xlat2.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat3.xy,u_xlat3.z);
    u_xlat2.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat3.xy,u_xlat3.z);
    u_xlat2.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_17 = dot(u_xlat2, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_33 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_33;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb0 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_17 = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_17;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_17) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD8.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_0.wwww + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_2 = -abs(u_xlat16_2) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2 = min(max(u_xlat16_2, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2 = clamp(u_xlat16_2, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + (-_colorSkin.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _colorSkin.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_2, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_53 = dot(u_xlat16_2, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_3.w + u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 + u_xlat16_2.w;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_2.w + (-u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_6.x + u_xlat16_52;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_52 = min(max(u_xlat16_52, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_52 = clamp(u_xlat16_52, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 2.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xzw) * vec3(u_xlat16_52) + u_xlat16_1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xw = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _shapeST.xy + _shapeST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xw).x;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_54 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_54 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_54);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_54) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_11.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_11.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_3.w + (-u_xlat16_53);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_54 + u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_54 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_53 = max(u_xlat16_53, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_53 = min(u_xlat16_53, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_53) * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat2.zw = vec2(u_xlat16_53) * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat2.xyyw * u_xlat2.xyxz;
    u_xlat16.xy = u_xlat2.zw * u_xlat2.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat48 / u_xlat10.y;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat48 / u_xlat16.y;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat51;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz / u_xlat8.zzz;
    u_xlat15.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BumpMapNr2_ST.xy + _BumpMapNr2_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = texture(_BumpMapNr2, u_xlat15.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * vec3(-1.0, -1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + (-u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_55 = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_55 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_55);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_55) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.z;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = max(u_xlat8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat16.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat32 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = max(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _HairMap_ST.xy + _HairMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xy).y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.x = log2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat0.x = exp2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot((-u_xlat13.xyz), u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * (-u_xlat16_5.xxx) + (-u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = abs(u_xlat16_7.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(u_xlat16_7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat16_53) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_23);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_0.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_23 * u_xlat16_23 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_52) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_53) + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_53 + 1.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat51 * u_xlat51;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat48) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_5.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_52 = min(max(u_xlat16_52, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_52 = clamp(u_xlat16_52, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_52 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * u_xlat16_5.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xzw + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_1.xzw + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw * vec3(u_xlat16_17);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_54) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

SubProgram "gles " {

"// hash: 8983ad6f9ee3afb1
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD1.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat0.y);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat10_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _Mask * u_xlat16_1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_Cutoff);
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_17<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat2.z;
    u_xlat2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat3.z;
    u_xlat2.y = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat3.z;
    u_xlat2.z = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat3.z;
    u_xlat2.w = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = dot(u_xlat2, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_33 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb0 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_17 = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_17;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_17) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD8.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat10_0.wwww + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_2 = -abs(u_xlat16_2) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
    u_xlat16_2 = clamp(u_xlat16_2, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;

out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD1.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat0.y);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT

#extension GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod : enable
#endif

precision highp float;

};

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _HairMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _color4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _metalv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _roughv4;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShift;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _shapeST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _faceshadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _BumpMapNr2_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _colorSkin;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr2;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _HairMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec4 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
vec3 u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
vec2 u_xlat16;
mediump float u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
float u_xlat32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat48;
float u_xlat51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
mediump float u_xlat16_53;
mediump float u_xlat16_54;
mediump float u_xlat16_55;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _Mask * u_xlat16_1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_17<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_17<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat2.xy,u_xlat2.z);
    u_xlat2.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat3.xy,u_xlat3.z);
    u_xlat2.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat3.xy,u_xlat3.z);
    u_xlat2.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat3.xy,u_xlat3.z);
    u_xlat2.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_17 = dot(u_xlat2, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_33 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_33;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb0 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_17 = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_17;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_17) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD8.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_0.wwww + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_2 = -abs(u_xlat16_2) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2 = min(max(u_xlat16_2, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2 = clamp(u_xlat16_2, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + (-_colorSkin.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _colorSkin.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_2, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_53 = dot(u_xlat16_2, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_3.w + u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 + u_xlat16_2.w;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_2.w + (-u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_6.x + u_xlat16_52;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_52 = min(max(u_xlat16_52, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_52 = clamp(u_xlat16_52, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 2.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xzw) * vec3(u_xlat16_52) + u_xlat16_1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xw = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _shapeST.xy + _shapeST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xw).x;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_54 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_54 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_54);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_54) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_11.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_11.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_3.w + (-u_xlat16_53);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_54 + u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_54 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_53 = max(u_xlat16_53, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_53 = min(u_xlat16_53, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_53) * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat2.zw = vec2(u_xlat16_53) * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);

    u_xlat16.xy = u_xlat2.zw * u_xlat2.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;

    u_xlat32 = u_xlat48 / u_xlat16.y;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat51;

    u_xlat16_15.xyz = texture(_BumpMapNr2, u_xlat15.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * vec3(-1.0, -1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * vec3(u_xlat48) + (-u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat8.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_55 = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_55 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_55);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_55) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.z;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = max(u_xlat8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;

    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat16.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat32 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;

    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.x = log2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat0.x = exp2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot((-u_xlat13.xyz), u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * (-u_xlat16_5.xxx) + (-u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = abs(u_xlat16_7.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(u_xlat16_7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat16_53) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_23);

    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0);

    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_53;

    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_53) + u_xlat16_5.x;

    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);

    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);

    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat51 * u_xlat51;

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;

    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);

    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;

    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat48) * 0.125 + 1.0;

#endif
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_5.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_52 = min(max(u_xlat16_52, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_52 = clamp(u_xlat16_52, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_52 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;

#ifdef VERTEX

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD1.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
