UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr2;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _HairMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec4 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec4 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec2 u_xlat14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
float u_xlat28;
float u_xlat42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
mediump float u_xlat16_44;
float u_xlat46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
mediump float u_xlat16_55;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _Mask * u_xlat16_1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_15.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_15.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_0.wwww + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_2 = -abs(u_xlat16_2) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2 = min(max(u_xlat16_2, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2 = clamp(u_xlat16_2, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-u_xlat16_15.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xyz + (-_colorSkin.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_15.xyz + _colorSkin.xyz;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_2, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_2, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 + u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_16.x = (-u_xlat16_43) + u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_16.x + u_xlat16_43;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_43 = min(max(u_xlat16_43, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_43 = clamp(u_xlat16_43, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_16.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 2.0);
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_43) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xw = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _shapeST.xy + _shapeST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xw).x;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat42) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_47 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_8.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_8.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_47 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_47 + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(u_xlat16_2.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat16_2.xx * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat16_2.xx * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat7.xyyw * u_xlat7.xyxz;
    u_xlat14.xy = u_xlat7.zw * u_xlat7.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42;
    u_xlat46 = u_xlat42 / u_xlat8.y;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat42 / u_xlat14.y;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat46;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz / u_xlat4.zzz;
    u_xlat12.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BumpMapNr2_ST.xy + _BumpMapNr2_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = texture(_BumpMapNr2, u_xlat12.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(-1.0, -1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(u_xlat42) + (-u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_48 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_48 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_48);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat8.z;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat4.xyz = max(u_xlat4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat28 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat8.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = max(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _HairMap_ST.xy + _HairMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xy).y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD8.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.x = log2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat0.x = exp2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;

    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_44;

    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat0.y);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr2;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _HairMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec4 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec4 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec2 u_xlat14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
float u_xlat28;
float u_xlat42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
mediump float u_xlat16_44;
float u_xlat46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
mediump float u_xlat16_55;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _Mask * u_xlat16_1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_15.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_15.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_0.wwww + vec4(-0.0, -0.333333313, -0.666666687, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * vec4(3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946, 3.19148946);
    u_xlat16_2 = -abs(u_xlat16_2) + vec4(1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495, 1.03191495);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2 = min(max(u_xlat16_2, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2 = clamp(u_xlat16_2, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * _color2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _color1.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * _color3.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.www * _color4.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-u_xlat16_15.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xyz + (-_colorSkin.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_15.xyz + _colorSkin.xyz;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_2, _metalv4);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_2, _roughv4);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 + u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_16.x = (-u_xlat16_43) + u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_16.x + u_xlat16_43;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_43 = min(max(u_xlat16_43, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_43 = clamp(u_xlat16_43, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_16.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 2.0);
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_43) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xw = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _shapeST.xy + _shapeST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xw).x;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat42) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_47 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_8.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_8.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_47 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_47 + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(u_xlat16_2.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat16_2.xx * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat16_2.xx * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat7.xyyw * u_xlat7.xyxz;
    u_xlat14.xy = u_xlat7.zw * u_xlat7.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42;
    u_xlat46 = u_xlat42 / u_xlat8.y;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat42 / u_xlat14.y;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat46;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz / u_xlat4.zzz;
    u_xlat12.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BumpMapNr2_ST.xy + _BumpMapNr2_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = texture(_BumpMapNr2, u_xlat12.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(-1.0, -1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(u_xlat42) + (-u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_48 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_48 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_48);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat8.z;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat4.xyz = max(u_xlat4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat28 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat8.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = max(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _HairMap_ST.xy + _HairMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_HairMap, u_xlat0.xy).y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD8.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.x = log2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat0.x = exp2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot((-u_xlat10.xyz), u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x + u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * (-u_xlat16_6.xxx) + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_48 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_48 = abs(u_xlat16_48) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_48 = min(u_xlat16_48, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_55 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat16_55 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_0 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_55);

#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
uniform 	vec4 _lightDir;
uniform 	vec4 _color1;
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenResolution;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
varying mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_COLOR0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _color1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat2 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * u_xlat1.ww;
    gl_Position.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966) + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = 0.00999999978 / u_xlat1.w;
    gl_Position.z = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat1.z;
    gl_Position.w = u_xlat1.w;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;

void main()
{
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM float _FarWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _NearWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _OutlineMap;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);

    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = textureLod(_OutlineMap, in_TEXCOORD0.xy, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.w * 0.00999999978;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * _color1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat3.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat3.xx + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat3.zz + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat3.xy, u_xlat3.xy);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat9) * u_xlat3.xy;

    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat3.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;

    u_xlat2 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat3.xy * u_xlat1.ww;
    gl_Position.xy = u_xlat3.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966) + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat1.w;

    gl_Position.w = u_xlat1.w;

uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;

attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;

{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _color1.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;

    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;

    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;

    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat2;

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 300 es

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM

#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform

#endif

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _OutlineMap;

in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec4 in_COLOR0;

vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat12;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * unity_WorldTransformParams.www;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.yyy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_TANGENT0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat12 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat12 = min(max(u_xlat12, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat12 = clamp(u_xlat12, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat1.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2 = textureLod(_OutlineMap, in_TEXCOORD0.xy, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat2.w * 0.00999999978;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _color1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat8 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat8 = inversesqrt(u_xlat8);

    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;

    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;

Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
"// hash: 3b88408ef73e2427
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 _BaseMap_ST;
uniform 	vec4 _ShadowBias;
uniform 	vec3 _LightDirection;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
float u_xlat6;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BaseMap_ST.xy + _BaseMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _LightDirection.xyz * _ShadowBias.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = max(u_xlat6, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat6) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat6 = dot(_LightDirection.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = clamp(u_xlat6, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    gl_Position.z = max((-u_xlat0.w), u_xlat0.z);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    return;
}

#endif

#else

    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = max(u_xlat6, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat6) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat6 = dot(_LightDirection.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat6 = min(max(u_xlat6, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat6 = clamp(u_xlat6, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    gl_Position.z = max((-u_xlat0.w), u_xlat0.z);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_TARGET0;
void main()
{
    SV_TARGET0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
}

SubProgram "gles " {
""
}
SubProgram "gles3 " {
""
}
